data.description: Remodeled home in River Ranch! This 4 bedrooms, 4 and a half baths sits on the corner of Arabella and Biltmore Way. Easy walking to City Club, Pour, and all of River Ranch amenities. If you're looking for quality construction-this is it. Built by Lafosse builders, the home features Solid wood doors, Emtek & Top Knob hardware, Antique Pine flooring on the first and second level, St.Louis Brick, and Cararra marble flooring. Appliance package made to last-Wolf Range, Dacor wall oven, and Sub Zero refrigeration. The home underwent a complete remodel in 2021 with luxury finishes including Calacatta Gold marble, Quartzite, St.Louis brick, Visual Comfort & Eloquence lighting, designer drapery hardware, and custom shades. Additional upgrades include new paint inside and out, wood floor refinishing, new landscaping, balcony, and exterior columns. No space untouched! The master bath of her dreams and the garage space he needs (full 3 car garage!) The home has Bose surround sound capabilities in nearly every room, every bedroom has a private bath and walk in closet, his and her primary suite closets, multiple linen closets and storage capabilities. Schedule your showing today- This one could be what you've been waiting for!
